{"TopicId":162922,"ForumId":25,"TopicTitle":"Maneuverability Challenge - Reverse Flight and Crazy Ivan","CreatedByName":"sevenperforce","CreatedById":157695,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-05T16:59:10Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"sevenperforce","CreatedById":157695,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-05T16:59:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe challenge: Build an aircraft that can pull a Crazy Ivan.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you don\u0027t know what a Crazy Ivan is, watch this awesome scene from\u00A0\u003Cem\u003EFirefly\u003C/em\u003E:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo ipsEmbeddedVideo_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/J3rX0T2XNxs?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSimply, a Crazy Ivan is a mid-air 180. It works best with aircraft which have two engines mounted rather far apart and best if those engines are reversible. At full throttle, one engine is reversed, producing a dramatic torque that results in a 180-degree yaw. Then the engine is switched back to normal and the engines fire together, stopping the aircraft in midair and then taking off in the opposite direction.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ERules:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nAircraft engines only (no rockets)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nAircraft control surfaces only (no \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E or reaction wheels)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nMust be capable of normal rolling takeoff and landing\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EGoals:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nPull a Crazy Ivan\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nUsing reversible thrust on both engines, fly your plane backward\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nTake off and land backward or forward\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nGood luck!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bloojay","CreatedById":162865,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-06T09:38:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223112133\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022162922\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221499273950\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022157695\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sevenperforce\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n16 hours ago, sevenperforce said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAircraft engines only (no rockets)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRevoke this rule pls, Serenity\u00A0uses rocket engines that happen to look like Aircraft engines\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Joseph Kerman","CreatedById":176176,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-06T09:53:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe maneuver is impossible in real life; the closest you can get to the Crazy Ivan is the\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Herbst_maneuver\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EHerbst maneuver\u003C/a\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bloojay","CreatedById":162865,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-06T09:55:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/176176-joseph-kerman/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022176176\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/176176-joseph-kerman/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Joseph Kerman\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0Then it\u0027s a damn good thing KSP and Firefly are\u00A0the opposite of real life aint it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Joseph Kerman","CreatedById":176176,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-06T09:57:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223112879\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022162922\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221499334925\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022162865\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Bloojay\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Bloojay said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/176176-joseph-kerman/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022176176\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/176176-joseph-kerman/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Joseph Kerman\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0Then it\u0027s a damn good thing KSP and Firefly are\u00A0the opposite of real life aint it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI cannot even perform the Cobra with the Panther engines.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bloojay","CreatedById":162865,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-06T10:33:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223112881\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022162922\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221499335028\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022176176\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Joseph Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n44 minutes ago, Joseph Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI cannot even perform the Cobra with the Panther engines.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo ipsEmbeddedVideo_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022344\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/lIX50NlncQ4?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022459\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0Use yo gorram imagination, now stop cloggin this poor mans thread\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is my submission btw\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow if you\u0027ll excuse me I have to edit my OBS settings to be less... terrible.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-07-06T10:43:07Z\u0022 title=\u002207/06/2017 10:43  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 6, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Bloojay\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Etypo\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sevenperforce","CreatedById":157695,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-06T12:45:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223112877\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022162922\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221499334799\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022176176\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Joseph Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Joseph Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe maneuver is impossible in real life; the closest you can get to the Crazy Ivan is the\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Herbst_maneuver\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EHerbst maneuver\u003C/a\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s only impossible for a passively stable vehicle. All real jet fighters have\u00A0the center of pressure well behind the center of mass, and there is no way to invert this. But in KSP, with airbrakes and other drag-altering mechanisms, it\u0027s not necessarily impossible to get the center of pressure to change. Then all you need is off-axis yaw to do a 180-degree spin.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s why I also added the \u0022fly backwards\u0022 challenge. With some action groups, it should be possible to get a plane that can fly backwards or forwards, and if you can do that, you can definitely pull a Crazy Ivan.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223112867\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022162922\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221499333934\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022162865\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Bloojay\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Bloojay said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRevoke this rule pls, Serenity\u00A0uses rocket engines that happen to look like Aircraft engines\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe side engines on the Serenity are some sort of nuclear air-turborocket.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223112901\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022162922\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221499337211\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022162865\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Bloojay\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Bloojay said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo ipsEmbeddedVideo_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022344\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/lIX50NlncQ4?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022459\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0Use yo gorram imagination, now stop cloggin this poor mans thread\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is my submission btw\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow if you\u0027ll excuse me I have to edit my OBS settings to be less... terrible.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWow, gorgeous! Kudos to you.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sevenperforce","CreatedById":157695,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-06T12:57:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223112881\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022162922\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221499335028\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022176176\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Joseph Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Joseph Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI cannot even perform the Cobra with the Panther engines.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can perform the Cobra if I throttle down the Panthers so that \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Thrust-to-weight ratio\u0022\u003ETWR\u003C/abbr\u003E is \u0026lt; 1 without afterburners.\u00A0Throttle low enough that you have level sustained subsonic flight, then increase the throttle to max and immediately nose up to a stall before the Panthers have time to spin up. As soon as you stall, but before the Panthers have throttled up, hit the afterburner to immediately push your \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Thrust-to-weight ratio\u0022\u003ETWR\u003C/abbr\u003E over 1. Then you can use thrust vectoring to dance on your tail for a bit. Once you start to accelerate, kick the afterburners off and nose forward again.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}